OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSunny start for most but
OL,6,Fcloudier conditions with some rain
OL,7,Facross the Outer Hebrides spread east
OL,8,Fthis morning, although the south
OL,9,Fremains largely dry. The rain turns
OL,10,Fmore persistent and heavier later this
OL,11,Fafternoon, with risk of hail and
OL,12,Fthunder.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FCloudy with occasionally
OL,15,Fheavy and thundery rain, risk of hail
OL,16,Fand torrential downpours in south,
OL,17,Fthis evening. The rain clears
OL,18,Fsoutheast overnight with some clear
OL,19,Fspells developing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
