OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FA largely dry and bright
OL,6,Fmorning with some sunny spells but
OL,7,Fcloud increases from the south towards
OL,8,Fmidday. Outbreaks of occasionally
OL,9,Fheavy rain spreads erratically north
OL,10,Fthrough the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FBright
OL,13,Fstart Saturday with some sunny spells
OL,14,Fbut occasionally heavy rain spreads
OL,15,Feast in afternoon. Sunday and Monday
OL,16,Fsee sunny spells and showers with
OL,17,Ffresh southwesterly winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
